title: Joovy Twin Roo+ Car Seat Stroller with Chicco Adapters, Holds Two Car Seats, Stroller Frame
features: Includes adapters for two Chico Key Fit 30 car seats, car seats simply click-in
Unique side mount gives you easy access without stroller handle or second car seat getting in your way
Small wheel-base provides easy handling and super maneuverability
One-hand fold, front-wheel suspension, swivel wheel locks, rear brakes, and large basket

description: The TwinRoo+ (TwinRoo Plus) Car Seat Stroller with Chicco Adapters mounts two Chicco Key Fit 30 infant car seats sideways and in the same or opposite directions giving you easy access to your children without the stroller handle or second car seat getting in your way. Its unique design provides a smaller wheelbase for super maneuverability and easy handling. It features a lightweight frame, front swivel wheel locks, rear wheel brakes, front wheel suspension and a one-hand fold. Adapters for two Chicco Key Fit 30 infant car seats are included. The frame is wider by design to provide maximum stability for your babies. Car seats click-in and release with the car seat's release lever. It includes a large parent tray with four cup holders for bottles and beverages. The tray sits below with your child to avoid the risk of spills. The tray is still in reach while walking and even easier to use when sitting with your children. The oversized basket is great for diaper bags and other necessities. The TwinRoo+ Car Seat Stroller with Chicco Adapters is full of innovation and designed to make your life with twins easier.
